(81, 'Pelikan 百利金 Souveran 805 Stresemann Fine Point M尖', 1, 15120, 'The foreign minister of the Weimar Republic， Gustav Stresemann (1879 - 1929)， had an impressive political career. He also became famous for the creation of a new kind of suit with stripes. He liked to wear suits with thin stripes and as life sometimes goes， a legend developed. Soon there after， people around the world called striped fountain pens， \"Stresemann\".; To officially acknowledge and honor his legend， Pelikan has now named the latest addition， the Souveran with elegant stripes in anthracite， the \"Stresemann\". ; Stresemann Features:; Anthracite stripes made of cellulose acetate on barrel Palladium plated clip and rings Hand-crafted finely engraved 18K gold nib available in extra-fine， fine medium or broad nib sizes. Delivered in a beautiful Pelikan gift box The Souveran 805 has an oversized body for those who enjoy a substantial pen.', 'pelikan_081-1.jpg', '2024-03-10 00:00:00', '2022-11-23 00:00:00', 1),
(82, 'Pelikan 百利金 Souveran 805 Stresemann Fine Point F尖', 1, 15120, 'The foreign minister of the Weimar Republic， Gustav Stresemann (1879 - 1929)， had an impressive political career. He also became famous for the creation of a new kind of suit with stripes. He liked to wear suits with thin stripes and as life sometimes goes， a legend developed. Soon there after， people around the world called striped fountain pens， \"Stresemann\".; To officially acknowledge and honor his legend， Pelikan has now named the latest addition， the Souveran with elegant stripes in anthracite， the \"Stresemann\". ; Stresemann Features:; Anthracite stripes made of cellulose acetate on barrel Palladium plated clip and rings Hand-crafted finely engraved 18K gold nib available in extra-fine， fine medium or broad nib sizes. Delivered in a beautiful Pelikan gift box The Souveran 805 has an oversized body for those who enjoy a substantial pen.', 'pelikan_082-1.jpg', '2024-03-05 00:00:00', '2022-10-03 00:00:00', 1),
(83, 'Pelikan 百利金 Souveran M605 Stresemann Anthracite Stripes B尖', 1, 12600, 'Pelikan Souveran M605 Stresemann Anthracite Stripes Fountain Pen， Extra-Fine Nib， Black， 1 Each is a true classic in fine writing made in Germany dedicated to the foreign minister of the German Weimarer Republic， Gustav Stresemann， who also became famous for the creation of a new kind of suit. The elegant piston fountain pen is equipped with an 18-carat gold nib which is completely covered by rhodium to obtain a silver sheen. The barrel with the deceptively simple anthracite stripes is made of cellulose acetate， using a traditional process that is extremely work-intensive but gives this series its elegant character. Pen measures 13.3 cm with closed cap and weighs 16.4 grams. Easy to fill with no-mess Pelikan 4001 or Edelstein bottled ink.', 'pelikan_083-1.jpg', '2024-02-21 00:00:00', '2022-06-30 00:00:00', 1),
